Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see how you live in this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and the place where I'll be able\Nto do that is where I've decided to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I can see you from that place, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.19,0:00:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'll come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen! I'll go to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.23,0:01:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you knew I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I saw you walk by from below.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought you'd already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.59,0:01:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You called out my name, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.28,0:01:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward and\Nrepeat my desires in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.12,0:01:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I want to be in the places\Nwhere my voice can reach...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:42.46,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 7: Let Me Hear\Nthe Melody of Your Smile"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it about my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me what my brother\Ndid when he summoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he was giving me a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Like he was telling me to think about\Nwhether I was in a position to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's why he acted\Nthat way at the tea party...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the only thing I can't\Nfeel toward my brother is hostility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He said something terrible to you after\Nhe made me leave the room, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That man has no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he did, that doesn't mean\NI'd want you to go beat him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I let go without thinking, but I wanted\Nto stay in that position a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, will you hear me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,About me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...and my brother...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother was always in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Lord Brother\Nwas always in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When my brother turned 17...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A birthday present...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A castle would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,At the border of Lido and Sui territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Lido and Sui? Aren't they famous\Nfor having the two feuding lords?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you thinking of mediating\Nbetween them, your highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then why would you want a castle there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It just looks like a\Nnice place to build a castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It took a while before the young me\Nrealized the meaning behind those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to ingratiate\Nthemselves with my brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The lords of Lido and Sui started\Nsending him money and goods...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you for your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...and my brother readily accepted\Nthem as construction funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Before long, retainers from both men\Nhad come to talk with him in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to send you funds for your castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the lord of Lido has been trying\Nto take more from the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the same in Sui...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask your masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, rumors had spread\Naround the castle about my brother--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That he had thought of a new game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You look dissatisfied, Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the lord of\NSui banished that retainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like it. The one from Lido\Nhasn't been coming around lately, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "I wonder"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, Zen, why don't\Nwe go see how my castle is going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:06:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make some stops on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying that, he went to visit the two lords,\Nand let me hear him telling them the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know that the other lord\Nis using his people's money
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to try to ingratiate himself with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's foolish?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What good will he be to me\Nif his people are weakened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...something that foolish man would think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking this was a good chance\Nbecause the prince thought less of his rival,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the two lords stopped overtly extorting\Nmoney and turned to more unlawful means.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what my brother was waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He investigated the crimes of the two lords\Nand the people they were dealing with secretly
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and got rid of all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Lords who let their people rot should\Njust be attacked and killed in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:08:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Both lords lost their positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, my brother appointed the\Ntwo former retainers as their successors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been taking care of\Nthem at the castle for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And he returned the vast amounts of\Ntribute he had received from the two lords
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to be used as funds for the two lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother had not touched any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize, Lord Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were using the\Nlords as a means of amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was having fun, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they will hold a grudge against you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder. They might come\Nand attack me someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't have anyone to be\Nmy shield when that time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,then that was all I was as a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do not make those around\Nyou recognize you as the king's son,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you will not become aware of it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This person... This man was going\Nto become the king of Clarines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to become someone\Nwho could stand next to this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted that with everything I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it's gotten pretty late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, Shirayuki. There's one more\Nthing I needed to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,To me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Raj said something outrageous at the tea party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...was thinking of you as my fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone took him seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but it might be uncomfortable for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, everyone\Nwill be wondering about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can stay in the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Zen? What about Laxdo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, those guys will recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I remember\NI just shouldn't shrink from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation is easy to understand, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Really easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If the people around are watching,\Nthen you should just do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be easy to stick to\Nthat position for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone will always be on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki and the prince?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But those two don't seem\Nlike more than friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Where did you hear\Nabout this hot information?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from the guys who\Nwere on guard at the tea party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They said Prince Raj from the\Nkingdom next door said so, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Raj...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of person he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he knows\NShirayuki and the prince, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is... th-the tour of\Nthe medical buildings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not look well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, they look wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The best medicine is made\Nin the best buildings, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanbarun could learn from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Sakaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I am honored by your kind words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, please step inside--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's quite all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:12:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I would not want to get in the way of your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.67,0:12:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was ordered by Prince Izana\Nto show you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakaki, you check it out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't they say that girl\Nwas working as an herbalist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll I do if we run into each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. We shouldn't cause her\Nmore problems than we already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway. Nothing good\Nwill come of us meeting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Shirayuki feels the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Prince Raj? Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You get it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let us quickly embark on our tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What wonderful facilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... That's the storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Storage room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is fine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wow! This is too wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can finish by the evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the end of the checks, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,These past few days have felt really long, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki, what's after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just seeing Prince Raj off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you in a bit, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to see the Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Shirayuki's working right now, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Have you seen my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, did you have business with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to have a little talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally over...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't relax just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not leaving the castle until this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ow...\N--Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not faking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been expending too much mental\Nenergy recently, so my stomach hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have said so earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I could have!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stand it if those Clarines guys\Nthought of me as a weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Then I will\Ngo get medicine, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell them it's for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is to bring this\Nto the treatment room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it over then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Shirayuki is all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl close to Prince Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl with the bright red hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like it hasn't\Nbeen set in stone yet, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know. She seems to be\Nclose to Mitsuhide and Kiki, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It is exactly as Zen had said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be uncomfortable for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But Zen, this place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Brother, I would like to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Brother...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, let's spar a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to move around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Following that prince around\Nmakes my shoulders stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you aren't just here to chat, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. Start talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you treating Shirayuki as a\Nnuisance before trying to get to know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm too busy to\Nslowly observe a single girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so busy that you will reach\Na decision without knowing anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You've learned to speak up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because of the subject matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I didn't need any time to\Nfigure out how hard you'd fallen for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, leaving that aside,\Nthis has nothing to do with your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other girls who\Nhave more political worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,People will expect the girl to\Nbe more than just her red hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and once they realize there is nothing more,\Nthey will look at you with cold eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be doing badly today, Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl is good at acting\Nto break down preconceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not think meeting Shirayuki will\Nprevent me from reaching my true path!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then leave her behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you were by his side,\Nhe brought in a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's {\i1}because{\i0} I was by his side, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You have also become impertinent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:18:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like our master said\Nsomething impertinent, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he's showing his true nature, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that man doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he waiting for a hole to open in my stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It looks like you're working hard in Clarines.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like this is a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,D-D-Don't worry about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What, they just had you bring the medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why are you opening that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't this what I asked for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not! I didn't hear anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:19:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him not to say it was for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's topical medication! For wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh--? It wasn't stomach medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't drink it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say too much because\NI just had it lying around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But you are a prince, and this\Nis the castle of another country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to take responsibility\Nfor taking care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though my being a\Nprince doesn't help you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you can say something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, please become someone that I can\Nbe glad is the prince of my home country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be rude, but that is what I desire,\Nas someone born in Tanbarun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I know that without you telling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness! Please do not\Nwander around by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you were slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to see how you\Nare before prescribing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I accompany you to the treatment room?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait anymore!\NIt's because you were so slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The chief herbalist will get mad at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I saw the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you'd be better off with Raj, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd dislike being in a country\Nwith a man like me around, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Izana...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of going back to Tanbarun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't back off?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't avert your eyes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, princess? Have you come to dislike it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I never will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the country where I met Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What strange children.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't show up at the send off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:21:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:22:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakaki, bow once toward the castle for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The path I've reached...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The flag hanging as a guidepost...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My steps that continue forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As we hold hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That wind will never stop blowing through!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.34,0:24:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,His back, eyes, and heart were still young...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.56,0:24:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, I didn't know\Nanything about the burden he bore...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.53,0:24:20.06,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 8: Memories\NDraw Spirals of the Past..."
